From: Ido Yariv <ido@wizery.com>
Date: Tue, 30 Apr 2013 11:03:51 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 0743/1587] mmc: omap_hsmmc: add DT power properties

Allow passing MMC_CAP_POWER_OFF_CARD and MMC_PM_KEEP_POWER capabilities
from DT.

Signed-off-by: Ido Yariv <ido@wizery.com>
Signed-off-by: Eliad Peller <eliad@wizery.com>
[zou: Original patch taken from
ti-sdk-am335x-evm-08.00.00.00-Linux-x86-Install.bin]
Signed-off-by: Cao Zou <cao.zou@windriver.com>
---
 drivers/mmc/host/omap_hsmmc.c |    6 ++++++
 1 files changed, 6 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/mmc/host/omap_hsmmc.c b/drivers/mmc/host/omap_hsmmc.c
index 978f034..8b23465 100644
--- a/drivers/mmc/host/omap_hsmmc.c
+++ b/drivers/mmc/host/omap_hsmmc.c
@@ -1815,6 +1815,12 @@ static struct omap_mmc_platform_data *of_get_hsmmc_pdata(struct device *dev)
 	else if (bus_width == 8)
 		pdata->slots[0].caps |= MMC_CAP_8_BIT_DATA;
 
+	if (of_find_property(np, "cap-power-off-card", NULL))
+		pdata->slots[0].caps |= MMC_CAP_POWER_OFF_CARD;
+
+	if (of_find_property(np, "keep-power-in-suspend", NULL))
+		pdata->slots[0].pm_caps |= MMC_PM_KEEP_POWER;
+
 	if (of_find_property(np, "ti,needs-special-reset", NULL))
 		pdata->slots[0].features |= HSMMC_HAS_UPDATED_RESET;
 
